item.title: Where is teh noclip command in
item.dc:creator: @william1434 william1434
item.description:
@william1434 wrote:

[quote=“yakman, post:10, topic:79131”]im sure he means a deob

go to client.java, go to the main() method, around the bottom you will find something that looks like this

Class64.aString = "127.0.0.1";

change that to

Class64.aString = "jolt1.runescape.com"; [/quote]

Thanks you so much thanks thanks thanks
